text: I did some more testing with Invision Sync today. I couldn't recreate the error I got with Elise about the screen exports. I tested having multiple files and having artboards with duplicate names. Everything went smooth, however, when you have artboards with the same name the one most recently created or edited will overwrite the one in the folder. You can see all version in the history section online though.
